author: cms-tsg-storm
body:
#### PR description:

Development of HLT menus for `CMSSW_12_3_X`.

Includes the integration of the following JIRA tickets:

  - [CMSHLT-2214](https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-2214): update of MSSM-Hbb triggers for Run-3 startup
  - [CMSHLT-2223](https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-2223): removal of TriplePhoton triggers
  - [CMSHLT-2225](https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-2225): removal of obsolete Parking EndPaths

It also includes a fix for unreferenced InputTags missed in [CMSHLT-2186](https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-2186?focusedCommentId=4172121&page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels%3Acomment-tabpanel#comment-4172121), and technical fixes for a few Streams and OutputModules (related to the upcoming adoption of 'Dataset paths' and FinalPath).

#### PR validation:

TSG tests.

title: HLT menu development for `12_3_X`
